  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice + an on-device screenshot from the Flipper running\n     a calculator (it's on the Photo Day list). Draft until then. -->\n<p class=\"\">A set of minimalist space- and physics calculators for the Flipper Zero — relativistic time dilation, space-travel figuring, and friends, all on the 128×64 screen for back-of-the-napkin astrophysics in your pocket.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The orbital-mechanics constants and transfer math, in C on the Flipper Zero\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-space-calculators/code.png\" alt=\"The orbital-mechanics constants and transfer math, in C on the Flipper Zero\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/flipper-space-calculators/code.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/flipper-space-calculators/code.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-space-calculators/code.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/flipper-space-calculators/code.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The orbital-mechanics constants and transfer math, in C on the Flipper Zero\" width=\"1400\" height=\"900\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.06deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1400×900\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The orbital-mechanics constants and transfer math, in C on the Flipper Zero</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The transfer solver — delta-v, flight time, and a celestial-body database keyed by semi-major axis\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1